reviewText: This video is clearly listed as having English audio. Not true and no way to get refunf that I can see.
Good illustration, the story line was nice and uplifting.
Really enjoyed this story. As for being a princess movie it was good, and as always there was a certain way I wanted it to end. Either way it was a good movie. Oh and the music was perfect.
I saw this movie on Crunchyroll hopefully someday it will be on region 1 format.  It's an outstanding story of love, loyalty and duty.
